Sentencas: Cubic perovskite-type Sm0.3Sr0.7Nb0.08Co0.92O3-delta (SSNC) demonstrated excellent oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) activity at 600 degrees C due to a high concentration and high mobility of oxygen vacancies, which were derived from the low average cobalt valence and cubic structure in SSNC at room temperature.
